topics.body:
Shitty night last night.

Couldn't get a refill on my anxiety medication (it's kind of like Xanax but not as addictive).

That medicine suppresses a lot of my nighttime anxiety, so without it last night, there were 2 times where I almost had a massive panic attack (the kind that arise out of nowhere). Thank Satan below that it didn't happen because if it did, I would've really hurt myself, possibly suicide. 

I called my mom this morning to tell her what happened; she gets mad at me telling me how I am addicted/dependent on my anxiety medication and that's why I had all the anxiety last night etc.. >:( wtf
